SCARFOLDING FOLDERS:
scarffolding creates basic project structures so you can focus on writing the actual features or 
when and individual says "scaffold the folders", he meant creating the initial directory layout before writing the application logic.

e.g {
    bookstore/
├── backend/
│   ├── accounts/
│   ├── books/
│   ├── orders/
│   ├── payments/
│   ├── config/
│   └── requirements/
├── frontend/
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── app/
│   │   ├── components/
│   │   ├── features/
│   │   ├── hooks/
│   │   ├── services/
│   │   └── utils/
├── docker/
├── nginx/
├── scripts/
├── docs/
└── docker-compose.yml
}